item.title: Unbelievable! Learn the Secret Trick to Making Paper Airplanes That Fly Farther Than You Ever Thought Possible!
item.description: Introduction Are you looking for a fun and creative way to entertain yourself and your family? If so, you should learn the secret trick to making paper airplanes that fly farther than you ever thought possible! Definition of Paper Airplanes A paper airplane is a toy aircraft, usually made from a single sheet of paper or card stock, that is folded and launched by hand. It is a fun way to explore the science of flight and aerodynamics.
